To begin with, lets understand the controls:
1-indication of the heading of the aircraft, when entering values ​​through the keyboard, the course will be automatically set according to the entered data;
2-indication of the course of landing, it is the course of the approach line, when entering values ​​through the keyboard, the course will be automatically set according to the entered data; 
3,4-buttons for switching the circle to the left and right; 
5-button for entering the test mode, where you are asked to solve tasks of determining the type of entry into the HP; 
6-button for instructions that you clicked to get here; 
7-circular indication of the course of landing and sectors of entry into the HP; \ n8-circular indication of the course of the aircraft.
